text: Kansallis-Osake-Pankki was a merchant bank in Finland in 1889–1995. The bank's sign was blue squirrel. ==Chief executive officers== *Otto Hjelt (1889–1892) *Fredrik Nybom (1892–1914) *J. K. Paasikivi (1914–1934) *Mauri Honkajuuri (1934–1948) *Matti Virkkunen (1948–1975) *Veikko Makkonen (1975–1983) *Jaakko Lassila (1983–1991) *Pertti Voutilainen (1991–1995) Category:Banks of Europe Category:Companies of Finland Category:1889 establishments in Europe Category:1880s establishments in Finland Category:1995 disestablishments in Europe
title: Kansallis-Osake-Pankki
